### 登录
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"student","password":"123456"}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.token); %}

### 知识库列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/kbs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 文档列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/documents?kbId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 知识库概览
GET http://localhost:18081/api/workspace/overview?kbId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 当前模型与检索能力
GET http://localhost:18081/api/system/capabilities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 知识库成员列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/kbs/1/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 授予或调整成员权限（部门主管/管理员）
POST http://localhost:18081/api/kbs/1/members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"student","permission":"READ"}

### 文档解析详情与切片预览
GET http://localhost:18081/api/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 失败文档重新解析
POST http://localhost:18081/api/documents/1/retry
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 重建知识库向量索引
POST http://localhost:18081/api/kbs/1/reindex
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 新建知识库对话
POST http://localhost:18081/api/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"kbId":1,"title":"新对话"}

### 当前知识库的对话列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/conversations?kbId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 查看完整历史消息
GET http://localhost:18081/api/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 重命名对话
PATCH http://localhost:18081/api/conversations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"title":"设备预约规则"}

### SSE 问答
POST http://localhost:18081/api/chat/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"kbId":1,"conversationId":1,"question":"设备预约有哪些要求？"}
